Notes:
	Just an example of how we can use the text files to import EODHD data. 
	
	This focuses on bringing in all the German symbols and playing with just the XETRA Symbols symbol
	
	This demo presently ignores the fact that we'll need a syminfo mapping file, aliases and in fact
	the entire order submission process.
	

Import:
	DataSource:	EODHD
	IncludeList:	?scriptpath?\output\XETRA-symbols-rt.txt
	SaveAs:	xetra-symbols.rtd
	IncludeList:	Germany.XETRA {"assets"}
	
	StartDate:	2002/1/1
	EndDate:	Latest
	
Settings:	
	AccountSize:	100000
	DataFile:	xetra-symbols.rtd
	
Charts:	
	Price:	C